    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Inspired by classic late-90s exploration games with lo-fi horror atmosphere.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You came to photograph a castle. Now you need to escape it alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knocked unconscious and trapped inside an ancient fortress after dark, you realize you're not alone. Something here doesn't want you to leave. Your only hope: piece together the castle's dark history and find a way out before the spirits claim another victim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive. Solve. Escape</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evade supernatural threats</strong> - React quickly to avoid ghostly encounters as you explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the mystery</strong> - Examine objects and follow clues to understand what happened here</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate and collect</strong> - Find items essential to your escape while exploring twisted corridors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the past</strong> - Locate hidden bonus items that reveal the castle's dark history</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncluttered &amp; atmospheric</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a tight, hand-crafted mystery where every detail matters. Horror lives in the silence between clues and the shadows you can't quite see into. For fans of tense exploration and environmental storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to expect</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a solo dev project focused on exploration and mystery-solving. Think careful pacing, minimalist PS1-era aesthetic, and atmosphere over spectacle - not AAA production values. If you're looking for a 90s-style horror exploration game made with passion, you're in the right place.</p>",
